cting the bones or causing kidney problems.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029424,0.0417,0.056425,0.071025,0.084185,0.096121,0.10673,0.11248,0.11824,0.12234,0.1013,0.06002],"unified_progress":[0.036805,0.056759,0.07273,0.083773,0.092901,0.10082,0.1006,0.1027,0.10107,0.099495,0.085049,0.067303]},{"section":9,"text":"This guy doesn't seem to have those issues, so maybe not multiple myeloma.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.023779,0.03842,0.050704,0.062236,0.073625,0.087686,0.10167,0.11589,0.12709,0.12907,0.11185,0.077985],"unified_progress":[0.030734,0.052982,0.066193,0.075257,0.0854,0.090413,0.095367,0.10267,0.1044,0.11081,0.10108,0.084699]},{"section":10,"text":"Let's consider other possibilities.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.10146,0.082013,0.077801,0.071044,0.07439,0.078263,0.084123,0.095584,0.090322,0.062893,0.061513,0.1206],"unified_progress":[0.18908,0.071762,0.062039,0.063377,0.073765,0.075788,0.093722,0.089095,0.087244,0.071396,0.063849,0.058885]},{"section":11,"text":"There's something called extramedullary plasmacytoma, which is when plasma cells grow outside the bone marrow.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020761,0.037583,0.054266,0.072899,0.086383,0.10382,0.11736,0.12102,0.12694,0.13166,0.087492,0.039818],"unified_progress":[0.030667,0.05856,0.060983,0.09903,0.10739,0.10608,0.10752,0.10957,0.10271,0.095062,0.07208,0.050341]},{"section":12,"text":"It can cause a single mass like what we're seeing here.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025444,0.038841,0.049163,0.059791,0.071009,0.081998,0.093825,0.10149,0.11217,0.12686,0.1332,0.1062],"unified_progress":[0.033596,0.05294,0.066191,0.077721,0.086286,0.098868,0.09709,0.10056,0.10158,0.10052,0.097656,0.08699]},{"section":13,"text":"And since the bone marrow looks normal and there aren't any bone lesions, this fits.","dimension":8,"group":